                                        | Particles

                                p
                                    | A particle visualization produces a three dimensional scatter plot using three.js. The camera can be controled by using the WASD and arrow keys. Use WASD to move the 
                                    | camera's position, and use the arrow keys to change the direction of the focus (FPS style controls).



                                #particles-iframe(data-url="https://lightning-docs.herokuapp.com/visualizations/59/pym", data-pym)
                                
